        'The dealer\'s first two cards are a pair, which is the dealer\'s pair. The player\'s first two cards are a pair, which is the player\'s pair;',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents11':
        'When a pair appears, bet on "banker pair" or "player pair" to get rewards with corresponding odds.',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents12': '3. Any pair',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents13':
        'Refers to the first two cards of Banker or Player as a pair (see Banker Pair & Player Pair for details);',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents14':
        'Regardless of whether a banker pair or a player pair appears, the person who bets on "any pair" will receive a reward.',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents15': '4.Perfect pair',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents16':
        'It means that the first two cards of Banker or Player are pairs (see Banker Pair & Player Pair for details), and meet the conditions of the same suit and color at the same time;',
    'zr_cp_footer_menu_zr_zrtext_3_contents17':
        'Regardless of whether the banker or player has a perfect pair, anyone who bets on the "perfect pair" will receive a reward.',
